D-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%C3%B9ng-thanh/poem-JEwWLUc9JhHbaxGqyeGeEg">Tùng thanh - 松聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-thi-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Th%C3%A0nh/poem-enpEkZuUxBukUILt8WOLeg">Vịnh sử thi - Thạch Thành - 詠史詩－石城</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BA%B1ng/author-QGyhycNQKN2UVF9H-N6Zaw">Hồ Tằng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-%E1%BB%A8ng-V%E1%BA%ADt/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-thanh/poem-Iu2NPyiIdh88vcFlb34u_Q">Vịnh thanh - 詠聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi-%E1%BB%A8ng-V%E1%BA%ADt/author-XjaOXRT7NSnPjyRhhrtiSQ">Vi Ứng Vật</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
